Cleansing - 
A ritual in which the participants as individuals and partners cleanse the negative events, auras, memories, etc. from their lives. 
Expelling and burning, truth telling, forgiveness, cleansing.

Pledging - 
Exchaning of vows, pledges, and promises.  
Detailed vows, overall vows.

Love Sharing - 
Explanation of each partner's feelings and understandings of the relationship.
